Class SupplierQuarterReportData

java.lang.Object
entities.SupplierQuarterReportData
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class SupplierQuarterReportData extends Object implements Serializable
Represents the quarterly report data for a supplier. This class implements Serializable to allow its instances to be serialized.
